  "title": "beforeSearch hook for SearchBox component",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nFeature\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your use case for such a feature?**\r\nI saw a similar thing here,\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/823\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your proposed API entry? The new option to add? What is the behavior?**\r\nCould be\r\n```js\r\nthis.props.modifyRefine = refine => newRefine\r\n```\r\n\r\n**What project are you opening an issue for?**\r\n- react-instantsearch\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\n3.1.0\r\n",
